{"tid":2064102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那疫情突增36例！專家曝「毒株差異」：危機還在後面","createTime":"2020-06-14T14:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T05:28:34.000Z","uid":226955,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"6b973639468e138dc4d81c7b36dad5bd90f74a44","tid":2064102,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）疫情對全球造成嚴重衝擊。雖然疫情逐漸趨緩，但近日中國北京市卻在3天內新增了43例本土病例，顯見疫情有惡化跡象，令相關單位憂心忡忡。中國疾控中心流行病學前首席科學家曾光就指出，這次引爆傳染的「病毒毒株」跟之前流行的不同，因此提出警示，認為疫情有二次爆發的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1BqAVY8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1BqAVY8.jpg&h=2a4c77a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲肺炎病毒。<br />\n<br />\n根據陸媒《新浪新聞》報導，面對來勢洶洶的北京疫情，曾光就指出，目前北京疫情正在經受一次重要考驗，這次考驗可能是全國疫情相對平靜後最大的一次考驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ryFtwxF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FryFtwxF.jpg&h=4267b27b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲&nbsp;大陸疫情學家曾光。<br />\n<br />\n曾光進一步分析，基因測序的初步結果顯示，北京這波病毒毒株與先前流行的種類存有明顯差異。為了釐清病毒株的特性，目前研究單位已經做了兩例樣本檢測，還要繼續擴大檢測，這對判斷疫情走向有重要作用。更斷言，危機尚未解除，若沒有處理不好，恐將引起第二波疫情。"},{"pid":"c7fc5a646ffce61fca4a10f4cda9f28e1aa823b9","tid":2064102,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm